Find [imath] \lim\limits_{{n \to \infty}} \frac1{2^n} \sum\limits_{k=1}^n \frac1{\sqrt{k}} \binom nk[/imath]

Find
[imath]\lim_{n \to \infty} \frac {1}{2^n} \sum_{k=1}^n \frac{1}{\sqrt{k}} \binom{n}{k}.[/imath]
